4
00:00:06,590 --> 00:00:09,673
But Las Pegasus is a
wild vacation spot.

5
00:00:09,963 --> 00:00:11,864
It's just one big party!

6
00:00:12,067 --> 00:00:15,415
All those lights and sounds,
not to mention the crowds!

7
00:00:15,501 --> 00:00:18,153
Oh! Just the thought
of it is overwhelming.

8
00:00:18,486 --> 00:00:21,950
I know Las Pegasus doesn't seem
like either of your cups of tea,

9
00:00:22,209 --> 00:00:24,320
but I have total faith you
wouldn't have been called

10
00:00:24,344 --> 00:00:26,615
unless you were the perfect
ponies for the job.

11
00:00:26,960 --> 00:00:28,800
Probably not as
bad as we think.

12
00:00:28,904 --> 00:00:31,329
It can't just be
a loud obnoxious party

13
00:00:31,347 --> 00:00:33,193
all the time... right?

14
00:00:35,230 --> 00:00:38,701
Uh, Applejack. It isn't
as bad as we thought.

15
00:00:38,953 --> 00:00:42,289
PARTY ALL NIGHT! WHOO-HOO!

16
00:00:42,658 --> 00:00:44,363
You're right.
It's worse!

